edu.uga.cs.rentaride.entity

Interface RentARideConfig

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable

    public interface RentARideConfig
extends Persistable
    This class represents the configuration parameters of the Rent-A-Ride system. Note that the prices are always expressed in Cents, not Dollars. This is a singleton class.
